        "setup": "Create your keys via the [Accounts API Demo Tool](https://apps.betfair.com/visualisers/api-ng-account-operations/). Betfair's getting-started guide says each account gets a Delayed key and a Live key, and that app keys are needed for API requests. To create them, log in to [Betfair](https://www.betfair.com/), open the demo tool, run `createDeveloperAppKeys`, and later you can view them with `getDeveloperAppKeys` as described in [How do I retrieve and view my existing Application Keys?](https://support.developer.betfair.com/hc/en-us/articles/360004130392-How-do-I-retrieve-and-view-my-existing-Application-Keys).",
